{"tid":2137659,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"禾確特：話球員唔著重足總盃說法完全是垃圾","createTime":"2020-08-03T05:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T08:44:19.000Z","uid":7439,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68a66646a1a8c459dfdaa0f5665982b5a161e09f","tid":2137659,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.daznservices.com/di/library/GOAL/77/67/walcott-arsenal-fa-cup_17thtz1f5to9m1mqnlgf6b9oy7.jpg?t=-1435875965&amp;amp;quality=60&amp;amp;w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.daznservices.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F77%2F67%2Fwalcott-arsenal-fa-cup_17thtz1f5to9m1mqnlgf6b9oy7.jpg%3Ft%3D-1435875965%26amp%3Bquality%3D60%26amp%3Bw%3D1000&h=316fad3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾三度贏得英格蘭足總盃的禾確特堅稱，話球員不著重這盃賽的說法「完全是垃圾」。<br />\n<br />\n前「槍手」、現效力愛華頓的禾確特回顧三捧足總盃的經歷：「身為英格蘭球員，夢想是可以踢足總盃，更不要說3次捧盃了。大家說足總盃已經不如以往受愛戴，但我認為這說法完全是垃圾。這是一個值得球員回味和爭勝的獎盃。」31歲的禾確特更說，想起在這賽事跟對手換球衣，還有在2015年決賽入波，以及幾面獎牌，都是他美好的回憶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/MindlessCarelessAsp-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FMindlessCarelessAsp-size_restricted.gif&h=a2dc131b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67c352b108602905654ea9a33b5fcf46b4423814","tid":2137659,"uid":12034,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"禾確診：我最期待的是踢英格蘭足總盃"},{"pid":"1562310da679ebdfaf1a9d5229ad7b0e0507158e","tid":2137659,"uid":116821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"禾仔唔忘本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaea251fe4038f44a2f75f5a954cf9c08107fff","tid":2137659,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"佢又想兜個圈話自己唔係垃圾"},{"pid":"267ab9d287ea94da5c92185a2efb81f025e460c4","tid":2137659,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06: